1330
01:39:37,722 --> 01:39:40,642
(woman chanting) Kitana, our queen!

1331
01:39:42,394 --> 01:39:45,814
Kitana, our queen!

1332
01:39:46,606 --> 01:39:50,068
(citizens chanting) Kitana, our queen!

1333
01:39:50,568 --> 01:39:52,779
(continues chanting)

1334
01:40:01,121 --> 01:40:02,372
(triumphant music playing)

1335
01:40:18,471 --> 01:40:20,265
(Johnny) You want to know
what makes a hero?

1336
01:40:22,183 --> 01:40:23,685
(sweeping music playing)

1337
01:40:25,145 --> 01:40:26,479
It's not destiny.

1338
01:40:27,188 --> 01:40:28,898
It's not something you're born with.

1339
01:40:31,359 --> 01:40:33,527
It's discovering that sometimes

1340
01:40:33,528 --> 01:40:35,070
even one small light

1341
01:40:35,071 --> 01:40:37,449
is enough to hold back the darkness.

1342
01:40:39,159 --> 01:40:40,827
It's facing unimaginable loss...

1343
01:40:43,496 --> 01:40:46,124
and finding peace on the other side.

1344
01:40:55,383 --> 01:40:57,886
It's lifting up
the ones you love, knowing...

1345
01:41:00,930 --> 01:41:04,434
that they'll be there
to catch you when you fall.

1346
01:41:10,815 --> 01:41:12,650
It's searching for greatness,

1347
01:41:15,111 --> 01:41:18,990
then realizing you've had it
in you this entire time.

1348
01:41:20,909 --> 01:41:23,076
I say all of this to Raiden

1349
01:41:23,077 --> 01:41:26,456
and he looks at me and he says...

1350
01:41:27,165 --> 01:41:31,961
(imitating Raiden) "You...
You have taught us so much, Mr. Cage.

1351
01:41:32,962 --> 01:41:37,133
Thank you. Thank you
for sharing your wisdom."

1352
01:41:38,092 --> 01:41:39,803
And you know what I tell him?

1353
01:41:40,428 --> 01:41:41,638
What did you say?

1354
01:41:42,180 --> 01:41:44,182
I said, "That ain't no wisdom, bub.

1355
01:41:44,682 --> 01:41:47,352
That's perspective."

1356
01:41:47,977 --> 01:41:49,312
(children laugh)

1357
01:41:49,437 --> 01:41:52,565
(Raiden) Strange.
That is not how I remember it.

1358
01:41:53,733 --> 01:41:55,068
Oh. Yo.

1359
01:41:55,735 --> 01:41:57,569
I was just telling these guys

1360
01:41:57,570 --> 01:42:00,322
how we saved all the realms, together.

1361
01:42:00,323 --> 01:42:01,449
Oh.

1362
01:42:01,950 --> 01:42:02,951
(Johnny) All right. Look...

1363
01:42:03,701 --> 01:42:07,288
I may have taken one or two
creative liberties.

1364
01:42:08,081 --> 01:42:09,082
Behold!

1365
01:42:09,582 --> 01:42:12,961
The human female you rescued
from the pit of spikes.

1366
01:42:13,837 --> 01:42:14,754
Seriously?

1367
01:42:15,463 --> 01:42:17,173
Two or three creative liberties.

1368
01:42:17,674 --> 01:42:18,882
(Sonya) You know,
I've got to give it to you,

1369
01:42:18,883 --> 01:42:20,676
I thought you'd go
running back to Hollywood

1370
01:42:20,677 --> 01:42:21,760
first chance you got.

1371
01:42:21,761 --> 01:42:24,012
I made a promise to these guys.

1372
01:42:24,013 --> 01:42:25,639
Hollywood can wait.

1373
01:42:25,640 --> 01:42:26,641
(portal whooshing)

1374
01:42:27,642 --> 01:42:28,643
(Johnny) Oh, shit.

1375
01:42:29,727 --> 01:42:31,144
Tell me there's not another tournament.

1376
01:42:31,145 --> 01:42:33,397
No. Outworld has been defeated.

1377
01:42:33,398 --> 01:42:34,566
Earthrealm has been saved.

1378
01:42:35,733 --> 01:42:38,777
So, uh, what the fuck
are you doing here?

1379
01:42:38,778 --> 01:42:41,530
We have lost far too many
of our champions.

1380
01:42:41,531 --> 01:42:43,574
It's time to bring them home.

1381
01:42:43,575 --> 01:42:44,868
(lightning crackles)

1382
01:42:45,743 --> 01:42:47,495
Someone order a Necromancer?

1383
01:42:48,037 --> 01:42:50,122
He might look like Voldemort's nut sack,

1384
01:42:50,123 --> 01:42:52,500
but trust me, we're going
to need this fucker.

1385
01:42:53,793 --> 01:42:57,130
Hey, g'day, Blondie. Long time no see.

1386
01:42:58,381 --> 01:43:00,173
You ready for your next lesson?

1387
01:43:00,174 --> 01:43:02,552
For the glory of Johnny Fucking Cage.

1388
01:43:04,137 --> 01:43:05,513
(Baraka grunts)

1389
01:43:06,055 --> 01:43:08,725
Let's go get our friends.
Then we kill Kano.

1390
01:43:10,894 --> 01:43:12,436
Yeah. Good.

1391
01:43:12,437 --> 01:43:13,897
(heroic music playing)

1392
01:43:25,658 --> 01:43:26,742
(crackles)

1393
01:43:26,743 --> 01:43:29,120
("Techno Syndrome
by The Immortals playing)

1394
01:43:30,496 --> 01:43:32,582
(announcer)
♪ Mortal Kombat! ♪

1395
